# 4. Authentication Module

## Features

* Register User
* Login
* Forgot Password
* Reset Password
* Change Password
* JWT Authentication

### API Endpoints

POST /api/auth/register

POST /api/auth/login

POST /api/auth/forgot-password

POST /api/auth/reset-password

POST /api/auth/change-password

---

# 5. User Module

## Features

* Create Employee
* Update Employee
* Delete Employee
* View Employee
* Search Employee
* Pagination

### Employee Fields

employeeId

firstName

lastName

email

phone

gender

dob

designation

department

salary

joiningDate

status

profileImage

address

emergencyContact

---

### APIs

GET /api/employees

GET /api/employees/:id

POST /api/employees

PUT /api/employees/:id

DELETE /api/employees/:id

---

# 6. Department Module

### Fields

departmentName

departmentCode

manager

description

status

### APIs

GET /api/departments

POST /api/departments

PUT /api/departments/:id

DELETE /api/departments/:id

